      <t:body>
         
         <t:div type="edition">
           <t:note>
             This division into textparts and incipits follow <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient757">London, British Library, BL Oriental 757</t:ref>
           </t:note>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="IsaiahOfScete">
             <t:label>Extract from Isaiah of Scete</t:label>
             <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                 ጥንተ፡ ቃል፡ እምነገረ፡ ጻድቅ፡ ኢሳይያስ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ አነ፡ በ፩ጊዜ፡ እምጊዜያት፡ ንቡረ፡ በጥቃ፡ ገቦሁ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ መቃርዮስ፡
                 መጽኡ፡ ጉባዔ፡ አኃው፡ እምሀገረ፡ እስክንድርያ። ከመ፡ ይስአልዎ፡ ሎቱ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብሉ፡ ንግረነ፡ ኦአቡነ፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ንድኅን።
               </t:ab>
             </t:div>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="JohnClimacus">
             <t:label>Extract from John Climacus of Mount Sinai</t:label>
             <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                 ነገረ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ገባሬ፡ መንክራት፡ ዘደብረ፡ ሲና፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ወበ፩ እምጊዜያት፡ እንተ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ ንቡረ፡ ውስተ፡ ገዳም፡
                 ውሣጣዊት፡ ወመጽአ፡ ኀቤየ፡ ፩ እምአኃው፡ ለሕዋፄ፡ እምነ፡ ደብር፡ ወተስእልክዎ፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ሀለዉ፡ በደህና፡ በጸሎትክሙ፡
                 ወፈድፋደሰ፡ ተስእልክዎ፡ በእንተ፡ እኅው፡ ዘሰማዕኩ፡ ሕሠመ፡ ምግባሩ፤ ወይቤለነ፡
               </t:ab>
             </t:div>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Sayings1">
             <t:label>Sayings of Isaiah, ʾAbbā Bamnu (Poemen?), and Theodore</t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Albatariqun1">
             <t:label>Extract <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡ እልበታሪቁን፡</t:foreign></t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Sayings2">
             <t:label>Sayings of Poemen <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">አብ፡ ባውሚን፡</t:foreign>, Pachomius
           <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">አቡነ፡ ጳኩሚስ፡</t:foreign>, and other Egyptian Fathers.
              </t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Albatariqun2">
             <t:label>Extract <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡ እልበታሪቁን፡</t:foreign>
           </t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="JohnCrysostom">
             <t:label>Extract from John Chrysostom on the Gospel of St John</t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Theodosius">
             <t:label>Extract from Theodosius</t:label>
             <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                 ቴዎዶስዮስ፡ ዘየአቢ፡ ዘአስቈባኒ፡ ሶበ፡ ሐለየ፡ በሕሊናሁ፡ ቃለ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ዘይብል፡ እስመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ኮነ፡ ይትጌበር፡ መዓልተ፡
                 ወሌሊተ፡ ከመ፡ ኢይኩን፡ ክበደ፡ ለመኑሂ፡ ወኮነት፡ ተግባረ፡ እዴሁ፡ ተአክሎ፡ ሎቱ።
               </t:ab>
             </t:div>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Gannata">
             <t:label>Extract from <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">እምገነተ፡ አበው፡</t:foreign>
           </t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Zena">
             <t:label>Extract from <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">እምዜና፡ አብ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡</t:foreign></t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Evagrius1" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2121OntheE">
             <t:label>Evagrius on the eight evil passions</t:label>
           </t:div>
           <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Evagrius2" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2121OntheE">
             <t:label>Extract from Evagrius</t:label>
           </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
